## 🏗️ Architecture

### BRONZE LAYER 🔵
Raw customer and order data loaded as-is
- 5 customer records
- 6 order transactions
- Issues: Duplicates, NULLs, formatting

### SILVER LAYER 🟣
Cleaned and standardized data
- Duplicates removed
- Text standardized (UPPERCASE, lowercase)
- Missing values fixed
- Ready for aggregation

### GOLD LAYER 🟡
Business-ready analytics tables
- Customer segments (Low/Medium/High Value)
- Revenue metrics calculated
- Health scores assigned
- Ready for dashboards

