## 📋 Project Notebooks

### 1️⃣ Data Validation (01_data_validation.py)
- Detects duplicate customers
- Finds missing values
- Validates email format
- Creates quality report

**Output:** Quality issues identified before processing

### 2️⃣ Data Cleaning (02_data_cleaning.py)
- Removes duplicates using window functions
- Standardizes text (UPPERCASE, lowercase)
- Fixes missing phone numbers
- Adds processing metadata

**Output:** 5 clean, standardized customer records

### 3️⃣ Aggregations & Segments (03_aggregations.py)
- Joins customers with orders
- Calculates metrics (spent, orders, averages)
- Creates customer segments
- Assigns health scores (1-10)

**Output:** Business-ready customer table with segments

### 4️⃣ SQL Verification (04_final_verification_sql.py)
- Verifies row counts at each layer
- Confirms data progression
- Validates transformations

**Output:** ✅ All layers verified

### 5️⃣ Summary Report (05_final_summary_report.py)
- Shows data quality improvements
- Displays business insights
- Creates statistics

**Output:** Executive summary report

