## 🚀 How to Run

### Prerequisites
- Free Databricks account: https://databricks.com/try
- 30 minutes

### Quick Start

**1. Create Project Structure:**
```sql
CREATE CATALOG IF NOT EXISTS my_data_project;
CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS my_data_project.bronze;
CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS my_data_project.silver;
CREATE SCHEMA IF NOT EXISTS my_data_project.gold;
```

**2. Load Sample Data:**
Copy SQL from data/bronze_schema.sql and run in Databricks

**3. Run Notebooks in Order:**
- 01_data_validation.py
- 02_data_cleaning.py
- 03_aggregations.py
- 04_final_verification_sql.py
- 05_final_summary_report.py

**4. View Results:**
```sql
SELECT * FROM my_data_project.gold.customer_segments
ORDER BY total_spent DESC;
```

✅ Done! You have a working data pipeline!

